{"tid":1109312,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"心穎：唔好扮嘢啦！屌你！兜鳩左我先？","createTime":"2019-04-16T08:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T09:32:57.000Z","uid":14503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d36b28cde95834a2aa90b02e45ce6f5fcee71740","tid":1109312,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"心諗：緊係兜左你先快撚d落車啦，我要同安仔去扑野呀！<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n心穎：sosad...我好悶(我好閪痕)...教徒(我仲好緊快d插我啦好爽架)<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n心穎：...返屋企，唔好驚喎！(自動波架啦)<br />\n<br />\n哇 屌你好撚淫呀心穎BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OV7nbQ1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOV7nbQ1.png&h=0d2ea743&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0jdiv1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0jdiv1.png&h=49b653cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1ALT4n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1ALT4n.png&h=09395fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n51歲許志安（安仔）和鄭秀文（Sammi）經歷分手、復合到結婚，走過考驗才許下婚姻的盟誓，3年前黃子華為Sammi演唱會擔任嘉賓，就以「香港最後一個童話」來形容他們的愛情故事。 <br />\n今年是兩人結婚5周年紀念，不過，這個愛情「童話」，從今天起，或要幻滅了！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190416/large/1555386748_2903.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190416%2Flarge%2F1555386748_2903.jpg&h=0ec04c61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心穎上車即向男友人爆粗：「唔好扮嘢啦！X你！兜X咗我先？」 <br />\n<br />\n日前《蘋果》得到一條車廂偷情的短片，男主角是有婦之夫許志安，女主角是跟馬國明熱戀中的黃心穎，兩人竟然背另一半搞「安心偷食」真人騷！整條短片長約16分鐘，片段開首見到安仔、心穎和男友人坐在車廂後座，男友人堅持先送心穎返家，戴了黑色口罩的心穎竟爆粗反對：「唔好扮嘢啦！X你！兜X咗我先？」 <br />\n<br />\n安仔都撐心穎先送男友人返屋企，冧爆的心穎搣了安仔耳朵一下，再向男友人爆粗：「你住邊呀？X你！」安仔即叫司機開車往大坑，心穎得戚地跟男友人說：「佢（安仔）送我返去呀。」跟住蹺實安仔左臂，整個人挨在安仔身上撒嬌，兩人更各用手袋遮掩，悄悄地玩十指緊扣。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190416/large/1555386747_2366.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190416%2Flarge%2F1555386747_2366.jpg&h=05687e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男友人落車後，心穎即飛擒咀安仔。 <br />\n<br />\n約3分鐘後，男友人抵家預備落車，安仔：「而家你走先，跟住我返我屋企，佢（心穎）返佢屋企。」男友人：「你講堅？」安仔：「係，堅。」惟當男友人落車後，安仔和心穎異口同聲跟司機說：「鯉魚門（心穎香閨）」！ <br />\n<br />\n而被網民封為心穎BB的她，原來私底下竟是「世界級姣精」，終於可以在後座跟安仔獨處時原形畢露，馬上隔住口罩咀了安仔一啖，10秒後意猶未盡的她，索性除口罩埋身攬安仔啜嘴，表現猴擒。咀完後，兩人繼續十指緊扣，之後隱約聽到心穎說：「so sad...我好悶...教徒」跟住拉開安仔隻手不再緊拖，安仔惟有順勢將手貼在心穎大腿上，3秒後忍唔住又撩心穎十指緊扣。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190416/large/1555386747_3e4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190416%2Flarge%2F1555386747_3e4c.jpg&h=43dc8298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當安仔係攬枕 <br />\n<br />\n由大坑到鯉魚門短短10多分鐘車程，「安心」連環激咀逾20次，全程由心穎採取「主攻」情挑安仔，不停攬他狂打茄輪，其中一次纏綿遊戲錫了近1分鐘，咀到啜啜聲，熱情如火的心穎邊咀邊將手放在安仔腿部附近游走；當車輛駛入隧道後，心穎再次飛擒大咬狂咀安仔，咀完後忘形到連口罩都戴歪了，其間隱約聽到心穎說：「...返屋企，唔好驚喎！」"},{"pid":"494f45a9e10373e6e0d0a757a4d06bc2cf9fd3e6","tid":1109312,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ccbe5aafd56daa4a4d2435d64d150748b3483eb","tid":1109312,"uid":222392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:53:32.000Z","msg":"快撚啲啦屌，下面好撚痕呀！學是學非，明辨是非！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00b83e1d4b695862ecc10543986cd69ddf0d307","tid":1109312,"uid":14503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2ADuHt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2ADuHt.png&h=d4607211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n口技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58585a119bac418624bab2c11a9e51eb3d23f4d5","tid":1109312,"uid":14503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/117RPJk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F117RPJk.png&h=fb5f25fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前入個陣兩隻手大大力渣住佢條腰黎屌一定好有征服感。<br />\n男人偶像安仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馬明有得睇無得屌，心穎話自己係教徒wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcd591ee1fe13b2c7dd2b2b129c43a0e16df9c8","tid":1109312,"uid":38988,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:07:06.000Z","msg":"學鄭中基話齋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有邊個男人唔鐘意大波既女人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔係講蔡一智有幾大波<br />\n我只係想講個耶撚個機場有幾平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b6668054a6857af0098f112b193ad82f8de223","tid":1109312,"uid":14503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"喂！你唔好撚縮！<br />\n轉頭叫多兩個frd上黎開party!!!"},{"pid":"73c19db5ecdc9520c9a23069d0fba78da8ad83d0","tid":1109312,"uid":42509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f00b83e1d4b695862ecc10543986cd69ddf0d307","tid":1109312,"uid":14503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2ADuHt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2ADuHt.png&h=d4607211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n口技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"佢隻錶。係咪totally crazy黎？之前去問過要20幾萬。<br />\n<br />\n有睇錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5ef7f194478ffd26866664b7bd8cb7b420aa46","tid":1109312,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:32:57.000Z","msg":"推"}]}